Class Group

java.lang.Object
  com.apigee.sdk.data.client.entities.Entity
      com.apigee.sdk.data.client.entities.Group

public class Group
extends Entity

Models the 'group' entity as a local object. The group entity is primarily used as a way of grouping users, but can be used to group any entity.

Group entity documentation
